{"tid":1320300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癈老群組傳緊呢個活動","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:09:11.000Z","uid":50457,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"835f3802590d329af881a54f636ea98d782759be","tid":1320300,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;下星期六20/7/2019訂一個「我愛香港世界日」。在當日穿上紅色丅裇或手綁紅布或 絲帶上班或去街。不須要任何單張或旗。不須要遊行、在中國, 在香港，在台灣，在世界各地的香港人或熱愛香港而出一分力。去表示我們真的熱愛香港。不用粗言穢語、不用暴力。對每一個在當天穿上紅衣的人說聲我愛香港。我們要以無聲勝有聲，以和平和愛心去寬恕曾經破壞過香港的人。用我們紅色的愛火去溶解昨天互相的不信任.將昨天的仇恨化作團結的力量。向全世界各地去表揚香港的真善美。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，香港人多謝你&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n明顯針對21號民陣集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65b71cf7d2bb027a63510f371bb508be855b4fd","tid":1320300,"uid":214662,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾多人帶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f598568348059b75616d345047332c4785f9166","tid":1320300,"uid":94824,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"戴紅絲就係港獨<br />\n<br />\n全部見血"},{"pid":"0d840e360d4192705dfd9f982e1acb120594dc98","tid":1320300,"uid":191527,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"比盡你500慢人"},{"pid":"7aac62ff28e99a9886854e50db3343d7f4fa79bc","tid":1320300,"uid":54516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"又好似630咁打人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76df7253d979b7d8e5d2f4ce3944f72a6f1c681","tid":1320300,"uid":46371,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"[/member]20/7全民支持成立獨立調查組著紅色衫or 戴紅絲帶[/member]"},{"pid":"9b13742e8eddae9f16b1f2ee63432d3536d26524","tid":1320300,"uid":88366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:20:58.00